### Description

When changing the source of an image memory isn't released properly.

### Steps to Reproduce

1. Create a new page with an image.
2. Change the source of the image at runtime.

```
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using Xamarin.Forms;
using Xamarin.Forms.Xaml;

namespace Demo
{
	[XamlCompilation(XamlCompilationOptions.Compile)]
	public partial class Test : ContentPage
	{
		public Test()
		{
			InitializeComponent();
		}

		protected override void OnAppearing()
		{
			base.OnAppearing();

			Task.Run(async () =>
			{
				var state = true;

				while (true)
				{
					await Task.Delay(250);

					state = !state;

					Device.BeginInvokeOnMainThread(() =>
					{
						TestImage.Source = string.Format("Assets/{0}.png", state ? "foo" : "bar");
					});
				}
			});
		}
	}
}
```

### Expected Behavior

Memory consumption shouldn't increase significantly.

### Actual Behavior

Memory consumption increases significantly.

### Basic Information

- Version with issue: Xamarin.Forms.Platform.GTK 3.1.0.583944
- Last known good version: n/a
- IDE: Visual Studio 2017
- Affected Devices: Raspberry Pi Zero with latest Raspbian
